The paper deals with operations on terms and signatures, which are fundamental concepts in logic and artificial intelligence. The use of fuzzy equivalence relations and similarity measures is also a common theme in these fields. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). However, the paper also touches on topics related to automated reasoning (cs.AI), programming languages (cs.PL), data structures (cs.DS), and fuzzy logic (cs.FL).
